title: Brahms Lieder
description:
Elly Ameling had one of the most beautiful voices ever heard.  This album is a vinyl rip (I don&#039;t believe it was ever re-released on CD).  It&#039;s all piano accompany from Dalton Baldwin, so Amelings voice shines forth easy and sweet.  Her rendition of Von ewiger Liebe shows how Brahms could take you to cliff, throw you off, yet be there to catch you and gently bring you to Love&#039;s art.
